org.apache.juddi.v3.client

Class UDDIService

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.xml.ws.Service
      • org.apache.juddi.v3.client.UDDIService

  • @WebServiceClient(name="UDDI_Service",
                  targetNamespace="urn:uddi-org:v3_service",
                  wsdlLocation="classpath:/uddi_v3_service.wsdl")
public class UDDIService
extends Service
    The UDDIService is defined by the UDDI v3 specification as the Service from which all UDDI Ports can be obtained. All known ports: UDDICustodyPort, UDDIInquiryPort UDDIReplicationPort, UDDISecurityPort, UDDISubscriptionPort, UDDIValueSetCachingPort and the UDDIValueSetValidationPort. This class was generated by the JAX-WS RI. JAX-WS RI 2.1.5-b03- Generated source version: 2.1
